<h2>Christmas Sunday Service</h2><p class="eventtime">Sunday, December 19, 2010<span class='event-sep'>, </span><span class="eventTime">10:15 AM - 12:00 PM</span></p><p class="eventDetails"><b>Location:</b> Portland Christian Center, <a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=5700 SW Dosch Rd, Portland, OR US 97239" title="map it">5700 SW Dosch Rd, Portland, OR US 97239</a></p><div id="text"><p>Join us this coming Sunday as we celebrate Christmas on our official "Christmas Sunday" service.</p>
<p>The morning will feature a message from Pastor Ray entitled "The Grinch Who Stole Christmas". &nbsp;We will also be treated with some special Christmas music from our Portland Christian Center Choir &amp; Orchestra as well as a special number by our youngest choir, Tiny Tunes.</p>
<p>We'll also be blessed with some special baby dedications.</p>
<p>This Sunday will be a morning of celebration as we celebrate the birth of our Savior so make sure to join us.</p></div>